any worth following.\n\nAsymmetric Investing is built on proven frameworks and consistent analysis, which you can find here: \n💰START HERE with a Free Asymmetric Investing Subscription: https://asymmetric-investing.beehiiv.com/subscribe\n📈INVESTORS Can See the Market-Beating Performance of The Asymmetric Portfolio: https://asymmetric-investing.beehiiv.com/p/asymmetric-investing-portfolio\n🚀Invest on AutoPilot (home of the Pelosi Tracker): https://marketplace.joinautopilot.com/landing/3126/772780\n\n📈Fiscal AI is the best tool in finance. Try it now: ​​https://fiscal.ai/asym\n\n00:00 Google's XR Devices\n01:12 Recent Announcements and Features\n01:37 Google's Modular Approach vs. Competitors\n03:26 AI Glasses: Features and Use Cases\n05:52 Financial Implications for Google\n08:21 Final Thoughts"},"lengthSeconds":"536","ownerProfileUrl":"http://www.youtube.com/@asymmetricinvesting","externalChannelId":"UCM2udYo4m-_uQfbfLGwf6mA","isFamilySafe":true,"availableCountries":["AD","AE","AF","AG","AI","AL","AM","AO","AQ","AR","AS","AT","AU","AW","AX","AZ","BA","BB","BD","BE","BF","BG","BH","BI","BJ","BL","BM","BN","BO","BQ","BR","BS","BT","BV","BW","BY","BZ","CA","CC","CD","CF","CG","CH","CI","CK","CL","CM","CN","CO","CR","CU","CV","CW","CX","CY","CZ","DE","DJ","DK","DM","DO","DZ","EC","EE","EG","EH","ER","ES","ET","FI","FJ","FK","FM","FO","FR","GA","GB","GD","GE","GF","GG","GH","GI","GL","GM","GN","GP","GQ","GR","GS","GT","GU","GW","GY","HK","HM","HN","HR","HT","HU","ID","IE","IL","IM","IN","IO","IQ","IR","IS","IT","JE","JM","JO","JP","KE","KG","KH","KI","KM","KN","KP","KR","KW","KY","KZ","LA","LB","LC","LI","LK","LR","LS","LT","LU","LV","LY","MA","MC","MD","ME","MF","MG","MH","MK","ML","MM","MN","MO","MP","MQ","MR","MS","MT","MU","MV","MW","MX","MY","MZ","NA","NC","NE","NF","NG","NI","NL","NO","NP","NR","NU","NZ","OM","PA","PE","PF","PG","PH","PK","PL","PM","PN","PR","PS","PT","PW","PY","QA","RE","RO","RS","RU","RW","SA","SB","SC","SD","SE","SG","SH","SI","SJ","SK","SL","SM